description: Her hair was reminiscent of those fake cherries dripping with ethanol. Of course this was due to extensive use of dyes and hair products, and the bathroom counter was filthy. You were mostly just curious if her pubes were also the same color - never found out, she obsessively shaved. You probably only got to finger her once or twice before she rotated her inventory. There are no reasons.
name: Allura Peckar
